Subject: [PATCH 10/48] Add gRPC harness dropdown to Settings (oh-my-warp)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Settings → Features gains an 'Agent harness (gRPC)' dropdown listing the selected
backend's grpc_harnesses and persisting the choice via set_grpc_harness(); the
in-process bridge reads the selected grpc_harness. Mirrors the backend selector.
